Before I became the spoiler guy in the Bachelor world, my career was in sports talk radio.  Having worked in the Los Angeles market for almost 10 years, I bring a bevy of knowledge, insight, tips, stats, and gambling insight to this podcast.  So get ready for your daily dose of sports knowledge to get you started on your day with “The Sports Daily.” 

It’s a passion project of mine I’ve wanted to do for a while, and now, I’m finally making it happen. 

And remember, sports will always be the greatest reality show on television.  

Go search the link in Apple Podcasts or my IG story today, subscribe, & review as episode #1 is out now!
